{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PSH1jhTSxgqoPBZeJMhT8C","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Verification Proof: 10-5-migrate-consumers-to-stackprovider\n     2→\n     3→**Story:** Migrate All Consumers to StackProvider\n     4→**Tier:** unit-testable\n     5→**Date:** 2026-03-24\n     6→**Verdict:** PASS\n     7→\n     8→## AC1: coverage.ts — zero stack string comparisons\n     9→**Verdict:** PASS\n    10→\n    11→```bash\n    12→grep -n \"stack === 'nodejs'\\|stack === 'python'\\|stack === 'rust'\" src/lib/coverage.ts; echo \"exit: $?\"\n    13→```\n    14→```output\n    15→exit: 1\n    16→```\n    17→\n    18→Zero stack string comparisons remain. All coverage tool detection delegates to provider dispatch map.\n    19→\n    20→## AC2: otlp.ts — zero stack string comparisons\n    21→**Verdict:** PASS\n    22→\n    23→```bash\n    24→grep -n \"stack === 'nodejs'\\|stack === 'python'\\|stack === 'rust'\" src/lib/otlp.ts; echo \"exit: $?\"\n    25→```\n    26→```output\n    27→exit: 1\n    28→```\n    29→\n    30→Zero stack string comparisons remain. All OTLP logic uses provider dispatch maps.\n    31→\n    32→## AC3: docs-scaffold.ts — zero stack string comparisons\n    33→**Verdict:** PASS\n    34→\n    35→```bash\n    36→grep -n \"stack === 'nodejs'\\|stack === 'python'\\|stack === 'rust'\" src/modules/infra/docs-scaffold.ts; echo \"exit: $?\"\n    37→```\n    38→```output\n    39→exit: 1\n    40→```\n    41→\n    42→Display names, coverage tools, build/test commands all use provider methods.\n    43→\n    44→## AC4: dockerfile-template.ts — zero stack string comparisons\n    45→**Verdict:** PASS\n    46→\n    47→```bash\n    48→grep -n \"stack === 'nodejs'\\|stack === 'python'\\|stack === 'rust'\" src/modules/infra/dockerfile-template.ts; echo \"exit: $?\"\n    49→```\n    50→```output"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0167PgbvxGvH7NwRVf7SRSLy","session_id":"6707468c-554d-4568-9ea5-0d04d4a85f59","uuid":"9be330d3-7597-4a